    "asOf": "2008-01-30",
    "date": "2008-02-09T15:20:23Z",
    "text": "Clean Stove Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow individual taxpayers a tax credit, up to $500, for the cost of replacing a residential wood stove with: (1) a wood-burning stove that complies with current Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) standards; and (2) a pellet or corn-burning stove. Terminates such credit after 2010."
